addr="erct-001H">contractible</fr:link> type with centre <fr:tex>a</fr:tex>. For any family of types <fr:tex>B\colon  A \to  \mathsf {Type}</fr:tex>, we may define a function <fr:tex>\mathsf {ind}_{A,a}\colon  B a \to  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x : A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x : A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x : A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x : A}\right )\mathclose {}}}Bx</fr:tex> satisfying <fr:tex>\mathsf {ind}_{A,a}\,b\,a = b</fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
